                                        "text": "Introduce the topic and keywords of the lesson <b>(had (have), lamb, white, snow, followed (follow), school)</b>."
                                    },
                                    {
                                        "text": "Teacher plays the story book <b>“Mary had a little lamb”</b> from page 1 to 5, pauses at each page, asks students to listen to the story. Teacher reads the story again and teaches the vocabulary (<b>had (have), lamb, white, snow, followed (follow), school)</b>."
                                    },
                                    {
                                        "text": "For example: ",
                                        "list": [
                                            {
                                                "text": "At page 1: Point to the pictures and ask:",
                                                "list": [
                                                    {
                                                        "text": "<i>What is it?  &#x02192; It is a little lamb.</i>"
                                                    },
                                                    {
                                                        "text": "<i>What did Mary have?  &#x02192; Mary had a little lamb.</i>"
                                                    }
                                                ]
                                            },
                                            {
                                                "text": " Have students to repeat the keyword: <b>had, lamb.</b>"
                                            },
                                            {
                                                "text": "Ask students to repeat the keywords several times in chorus and individually and correct their pronunciation."
                                            },
                                            {
                                                "text": "Do the same in pages 2, 3, 4 and 5."
                                            }
                                        ]
                                    },
                                    {
                                        "text": "Practice speaking by using the structure: <b>I have …  and he/she has___.</b>",
                                        "list": [
