                                                "text": "Teacher raises an object in the classroom and says: <b>I have a __.</b>"
                                            },
                                            {
                                                "text": "Teacher gives each student a toy or object in classroom and instructs them to say a sentence:<b> I have___, he/she has ___.</b>"
                                            },
                                            {
                                                "text": "Teacher corrects their pronunciation."
                                            }
                                        ]
                                    }
                                ]
                            }
